 between ethnicization and pluralization, discrimination and empowerment, division and participation.The Yearbook Migration and Society repeatedly turns the prism of narrative anew. The 2022/2023 edition focuses on the topic »Climate«.  afunded by Alpen-Adria-Universität Klagenfurt  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aEnvironmental Policy. 4aEnvironmental Sociology. 4aMigration Policy. 4aMigrationspolitik. 4aNatur. 4aNature. 4aSociology. 4aSoziologie. 4aUmweltpolitik. 4aUmweltsoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Emigration & Immigration.2bisacsh  aEnvironmental Policy.  aEnvironmental Sociology.  aMigration Policy.  aMigrationspolitik.  aNatur.  aNature.  aSociology.  aSoziologie.  aUmweltpolitik.  aUmweltsoziologie.1 aAfeworki Abay, Robel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDe Silva, Malith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDonlic, Jasmin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDonlic, Jasmin, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFernando, Nishara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHollenbach, Pia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHuber, Ingrid, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIbrahim, Fazeela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIonesco, Dina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKanzian, Horst, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKromp-Kolb, Helga, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrüger, Marco, econtributor.4ctb4h